Stimulants raise histamine levels. Those with histamine intolerance or MCAS might not tolerate them well and may actually cause paradoxical effects like brain fog.
Ritalin can affect vision. Check the side effects, they include blurred vision and difficulty focusing. Let your doctor know.
Sounds like executive dysfunction which is a primary symptom of a lot of ADHD cases
